# Deployment Orchestrator

**Primary deploy entry:** scripts/v1/deploy.ps1

Do **not** use scripts/archive for deploy or CI; only scripts/v1. Archive is reference-only (00_ssot_v1_archive_structure.mdc).

**Deployment flow:**

1. Build image
2. Push ECR
3. Run deploy.ps1
4. Verify infrastructure

**CI:** GitHub Actions. Workflows may trigger ECR build and/or deploy.ps1.

Deployment must support **one-take deployment**.
